    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Barkskin</strong> (Level 2 Transmutation)</p><p>You touch a willing creature. Until the spell ends, the target's skin has a rough, bark-like appearance, and the target's AC can't be less than 16, regardless of what kind of armor it is wearing.</p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (A handful of oak bark.)</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> Touch | <strong>Duration:</strong> Up to 1 hour (Concentration)</p><p><em>Classes: Druid, Ranger</em></p>",
